author: Nexcell Pride
text:
Today, Rushia demonstrated once more she's good at cooking.
And that's the first time with Rushia streaming a formal edition of "Rushia's Cooking". :_ハート:
Before she cooked at special dates, like Halloween, St. Valentine's day and White Valentine's day.
Maybe a non regular streaming would be dedicated to cooking, today was a total success. 

According with some data from Hololive and Wikitubia, Rushia is proud of her cooking skills, especially at preparing seafood. :_きゅん:

Cooking Skills, a beautiful voice at singing and performing ASMR, also becomes an entertainment master.

Later of preparing the recipe and Supaachaato Orei Time, Rushia became more loving with her audience (Fandeads, fans and followers) :_るんるん:

:_ちょうちょ: Uruha Rushia's Original Character Design by Yasuyuki-sensei.
:_きゅん: Live2D modeling by Tou Ilie.
For more news, also contact with Yasuyuki-sensei and his secretary at Twitter: "yasu00kamiki" and "chiyogamimi".
